@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : ask to calculate total operational hours for each aircraft
activate System

note right of System: The system fetches all fleet aircraft\nand maps their registration numbers\nto their total flight hours.

System --> ATCC : returns the operational hours report
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml